From 878f5ee31ebb472e0fc9f52f6a68d5e8915a37a5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Balaganapathy Palanisamy <bpalanis@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Jun 2025 11:44:33 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] hostapd: Extend BSS_TM_REQ command to add partner links

Extend the "BSS_TM_REQ" command to add partner link candidates

Add following optional arguments to update the candidate list
with partner link information.

1. partner_link_pref: Add all partner links to candidate list with
provided preference value. i.e. partner_link_pref=5 generates candidate
list with preference 5 for all partner links.
e.g. "BSS_TM_REQ <STA_MAC> disassoc_timer=10 valid_int=20 dialog_token=1
pref=1 abridged=1 partner_link_pref=5"

2. partner_link_set: Add partner link set to candidate list
with provided preference value. i.e. partner_link_set=5,1,2 generates
candidate list with preference 5 for link_1 and link_2, where link_1
being the candidate BSSID.
e.g. "BSS_TM_REQ <STA_MAC> disassoc_timer=10 valid_int=20 dialog_token=1
pref=1 abridged=1 partner_link_set=5,1,2"

Signed-off-by: Balaganapathy Palanisamy <bpalanis@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
